<br>
snare spells are recastable - keep applying them, they have no immunity timer.<br>
<br>
PF is the same.<br>
<br>
However, if you root someone - the snares do not work at all - even though they'd not interfere with the root timer (or shouldn't)<br>
<br>
What needs to be done is make things that don't set immunity ignore it. <br>
<br>
I.e. if you have root immunity and are hit by a snare spell which doesn't set immunity it ignores that root immunity. <br>
<br>
